OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with occasional light
OL,6,Frain or drizzle this morning. Becoming
OL,7,Fdry and brighter for most places this
OL,8,Fafternoon with some sunny intervals
OL,9,Fdeveloping, but also perhaps isolated
OL,10,Flight coastal showers. Light northerly
OL,11,Fwinds inland, breezy and cooler along
OL,12,Fthe coast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells and patchy
OL,15,Fcloud, with a chance of isolated light
OL,16,Fshowers reaching coastal areas, where
OL,17,Fit will become windy. Becoming cooler
OL,18,Ffor many places, compared to recent
OL,19,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
